default&#xa0;
default9. It is unhealthy to declare any area of science finally settled: I welcome the fact that there are still
default a few scientists questioning the theory of relativity, although I feel no inclination to join them. Likewise, the fact that 
defaultgreenhouse gas emissions are
default having 
defaulta substantial
default impact on climate at a global scale is sufficiently well attested that further research into 
defaultalternative hypotheses is unlikely to be particularly fruitful, although it should 
